```csharp
.Options(o => o
	.Plugins(p => p
		.Filler(f => f
			.Propagate(true)
			.DrawTime(DrawTime.BeforeDraw))))
```

```js
"options": {
	"plugins": {
	  "filler": {
		"propagate": true,
		"drawTime": "beforeDraw"
	  }
	}
  }
```

## Propagate
Fill propagation when target is hidden.
```csharp
.Propagate(true)
```

